---
layout: base
permalink: /index.html
title: 'Plano Wildcats Hockey Association'
description: 'The official site of the Plano Wildcats Hockey Association — supporting Plano Senior High School hockey.'
news:
  title: 'Latest news'
  intro: 'Recent posts and announcements from PWHA.'
---

<div class="wrapper">
  <header class="full | section" style="--spot-color: var(--color-primary)">
    <div class="section__inner flow region">
      <h1 class="text-center" style="color: var(--color-light);">Plano Wildcats Hockey Association</h1>
      <p class="text-center" style="color: var(--color-light); font-size: var(--size-step-1);">
        Supporting Plano Senior High School hockey — Varsity, Junior Varsity, players, families, and alumni.
      </p>
    </div>
    {% svg "divider/waves", null, "divider" %}
  </header>

  <article class="full | region">
    <div class="prose wrapper flow">
      <h2>Welcome</h2>
      <p>
        <em>Phase 1 placeholder.</em> Replace this with the homepage hero copy.
        A typical hockey association homepage surfaces the next game, recent
        results, latest news, and ways to get involved or support the program.
      </p>
      <p>
        While we build that out, here's where to find what you're looking for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/schedule/">Schedule</a> — upcoming games and recent results</li>
        <li><a href="/teams/">Teams</a> — Varsity and Junior Varsity rosters</li>
        <li><a href="/history/">History</a> — program record, player database, alumni</li>
        <li><a href="/support/">Support PWHA</a> — donations, sponsorships</li>
        <li><a href="/about/">About Us</a> — officers, membership, by-laws</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>

  <section class="full | region">
    <div class="prose wrapper flow">
      <h2>{{ news.title }}</h2>
      {% if news.intro %}
        <p>{{ news.intro }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="feature |  region region-space-l">
        <custom-masonry layout="50-50">
          {% set itemList = collections.allPosts %}
          {% if itemList.length %}
            {% asyncEach item in itemList.slice(0, 4) %}
              {% set headingLevel = "h3" %}
              {% include "partials/card-blog.njk" %}
            {% endeach %}
          {% else %}
            <p><em>No news posts yet — once the demo content is removed and a real post lands here, this section will fill in.</em></p>
          {% endif %}
        </custom-masonry>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
